1
00:00:10,166 --> 00:00:11,584
(Sun Honglei)

2
00:00:11,936 --> 00:00:12,928
(Li Naiwen)

3
00:00:14,848 --> 00:00:16,416
(Guo Jingfei)

4
00:00:17,056 --> 00:00:18,880
(Liu Yuning)

5
00:00:19,328 --> 00:00:21,088
(Gong Jun)

6
00:00:22,240 --> 00:00:23,072
(Chen Xingxu)

7
00:00:23,712 --> 00:00:26,272
(Wang Yuwen)

8
00:00:26,592 --> 00:00:28,672
(Lin Yi)

9
00:00:31,882 --> 00:00:34,528
=Wow The World S2 Extra Episode=

10
00:00:35,328 --> 00:00:36,488
A foreign land.

11
00:00:36,488 --> 00:00:37,608
An unfamiliar language.

12
00:00:37,608 --> 00:00:38,768
Different customs.

13
00:00:38,768 --> 00:00:40,048
Unexpected paces.

14
00:00:40,728 --> 00:00:42,128
With this uncertainty,

15
00:00:42,128 --> 00:00:43,048
our senses

16
00:00:43,048 --> 00:00:44,488
are easily drawn to what's new.

17
00:00:45,088 --> 00:00:46,928
Besides, we're used to relying on

18
00:00:46,928 --> 00:00:48,328
navigation, translation apps,
and travel guides.

19
00:00:48,328 --> 00:00:50,408
We often forget
that the most reliable tool

20
00:00:50,408 --> 00:00:51,528
is our power of observation.

21
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,216
The next mission

22
00:00:53,216 --> 00:00:54,400
is to help you

23
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:55,928
reactivate your observation skills.

24
00:00:56,368 --> 00:00:58,088
(Eliminate members by specifying tasks)
This mission is called Strange Killer.

25
00:00:58,088 --> 00:00:59,008
(Remaining five will discuss and vote)
Among the eight of you,

26
00:00:59,008 --> 00:01:01,048
(Killer wins if the identity is hidden successfully)
there is a Strange Killer.

27
00:01:01,048 --> 00:01:01,968
(Or other members win)
During the meal,

28
00:01:01,968 --> 00:01:03,168
the Strange Killer must complete

29
00:01:03,168 --> 00:01:04,648
the assigned tasks.

30
00:01:04,648 --> 00:01:06,088
Each time a task is completed,

31
00:01:06,088 --> 00:01:07,648
one member gets eliminated.

32
00:01:07,888 --> 00:01:09,128
The eliminated member

33
00:01:09,128 --> 00:01:10,728
must stop eating immediately.

34
00:01:10,728 --> 00:01:12,448
When only five players remain,

35
00:01:12,448 --> 00:01:13,968
you can form a discussion

36
00:01:13,968 --> 00:01:15,528
to find the Strange Killer.

37
00:01:16,048 --> 00:01:18,848
If the Strange Killer
conceals their identity,

38
00:01:18,848 --> 00:01:19,808
they win.

39
00:01:19,808 --> 00:01:21,728
(Predicting the tasks)
Eat a banana

40
00:01:21,728 --> 00:01:22,608
with the peel on.

41
00:01:22,608 --> 00:01:23,608
Do a handstand.

42
00:01:23,608 --> 00:01:25,208
I'd rather slap myself.

43
00:01:25,208 --> 00:01:26,336
(Playing this big?)

44
00:01:26,928 --> 00:01:27,968
I ate too much again today.

45
00:01:31,768 --> 00:01:32,928
Please draw your roles.

46
00:01:33,152 --> 00:01:34,560
(Strange Killer: Round 1)

47
00:01:34,688 --> 00:01:36,224
(Drawing roles)

48
00:01:43,408 --> 00:01:44,408
Nai, it's you, huh?

49
00:01:44,408 --> 00:01:45,288
Of course not.

50
00:01:45,768 --> 00:01:47,048
It's written all over your face.

51
00:01:49,856 --> 00:01:52,448
(Scanning with eyes)

52
00:01:56,648 --> 00:01:57,568
Why are you smiling?

53
00:01:57,968 --> 00:01:59,608
I'm naturally cheerful.

54
00:01:59,608 --> 00:02:01,808
Okay, a born ray of sunshine.

55
00:02:01,984 --> 00:02:04,208
Everyone, please close your eyes.

56
00:02:06,168 --> 00:02:08,448
Strange Killer, please open your eyes.

57
00:02:09,984 --> 00:02:11,448
(This round's Strange Killer: Lin Yi)

58
00:02:11,448 --> 00:02:13,928
Strange Killer, please check your task.

59
00:02:16,192 --> 00:02:21,952
(Put an unshelled sunflower seed
in your mouth and point at someone)

60
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,344
(Tsk)

61
00:02:29,728 --> 00:02:32,128
Why make that kind of noise?

62
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:33,608
It's a cover-up.

63
00:02:34,528 --> 00:02:35,928
Still reading it, right?

64
00:02:36,728 --> 00:02:37,288
Yuwen.

65
00:02:37,688 --> 00:02:38,968
Let's slow it down.

66
00:02:38,968 --> 00:02:39,288
Yeah.

67
00:02:39,288 --> 00:02:40,648
My eyesight isn't great.

68
00:02:44,888 --> 00:02:46,608
Three, two, one.

69
00:02:46,608 --> 00:02:47,368
Please open your eyes.

70
00:02:48,416 --> 00:02:55,208
(Strange Killer)

71
00:02:55,208 --> 00:02:57,248
Everyone, please get started.

72
00:02:57,248 --> 00:02:58,088
Let's eat.

73
00:03:00,928 --> 00:03:01,504
(Juicy)

74
00:03:02,592 --> 00:03:03,408
(Lost in thought)

75
00:03:03,408 --> 00:03:04,728
It squirted out.

76
00:03:05,768 --> 00:03:06,928
Is this your...

77
00:03:07,450 --> 00:03:09,024
(Framing someone)

78
00:03:09,128 --> 00:03:09,928
Did something

79
00:03:09,928 --> 00:03:10,848
happen to me?

80
00:03:11,288 --> 00:03:12,248
No.

81
00:03:13,128 --> 00:03:14,088
The way you peeled that kiwi

82
00:03:14,088 --> 00:03:15,168
is too strange.

83
00:03:15,168 --> 00:03:16,888
You didn't get a napkin
when you ate the kiwi.

84
00:03:16,888 --> 00:03:17,368
Yeah.

85
00:03:18,168 --> 00:03:19,848
The juice squirted.

86
00:03:20,155 --> 00:03:21,696
(Pinned it on her)

87
00:03:22,496 --> 00:03:23,696
Yuwen, why were you smiling earlier?

88
00:03:24,136 --> 00:03:25,136
(Prime suspect)
I love to smile.

89
00:03:25,576 --> 00:03:27,856
Lucky girls are the ones who smile.

90
00:03:28,376 --> 00:03:30,336
You drew the role, right?

91
00:03:30,776 --> 00:03:31,256
Oh no.

92
00:03:31,256 --> 00:03:32,216
Statistically speaking,

93
00:03:32,216 --> 00:03:33,616
I can't draw that role.

94
00:03:33,616 --> 00:03:33,776
Wait.

95
00:03:33,776 --> 00:03:35,096
You're starting to babble.

96
00:03:35,096 --> 00:03:36,376
Don't you realize that?

97
00:03:36,376 --> 00:03:38,696
You even brought up "statistics".

98
00:03:43,136 --> 00:03:44,776
(Strange Killer Lin Yi)
Observe the others too.

99
00:03:44,776 --> 00:03:45,696
It's safe

100
00:03:45,696 --> 00:03:46,816
to observe you.

101
00:03:46,816 --> 00:03:47,376
No one has died.

102
00:03:49,984 --> 00:03:51,360
(Weapon loaded)

103
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:59,168
(Attack initiated)

104
00:04:00,536 --> 00:04:01,416
Fei.

105
00:04:01,416 --> 00:04:02,136
Put it down.

106
00:04:02,136 --> 00:04:03,136
You must stop eating.

107
00:04:03,696 --> 00:04:04,456
What?

108
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,744
(Confused)

109
00:04:08,249 --> 00:04:09,456
(Observing)

110
00:04:09,456 --> 00:04:10,256
Come on, Fei.

111
00:04:10,256 --> 00:04:11,296
Have a lollipop.

112
00:04:12,998 --> 00:04:14,304
(Mute mode)

113
00:04:14,936 --> 00:04:16,496
Why are you so quiet, Yuning?

114
00:04:16,496 --> 00:04:18,216
Don't you get hyper
when you are a Good Person?

115
00:04:18,216 --> 00:04:18,776
Yeah.

116
00:04:18,976 --> 00:04:20,000
(Tagging along)

117
00:04:24,296 --> 00:04:26,096
Why did you sneakily lean back?

118
00:04:26,336 --> 00:04:29,616
♪Silence does not mean I'm wrong♪

119
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:32,896
(Suddenly making eye contact)

120
00:04:35,456 --> 00:04:37,176
I can't see you.

121
00:04:37,536 --> 00:04:39,336
It's no use if you can't see him.

122
00:04:41,568 --> 00:04:43,424
(Weapon reloaded)

123
00:04:44,616 --> 00:04:45,896
Xingxu, how many grapes have you eaten?

124
00:04:46,376 --> 00:04:46,736
Three.

125
00:04:47,776 --> 00:04:49,536
(Doubt each one)
- Aren't you avoiding sugar? - Aren't you on a diet?

126
00:04:49,536 --> 00:04:50,496
Why are you eating grapes?

127
00:04:50,496 --> 00:04:51,776
- What's wrong with it?
- They're high in sugar.

128
00:04:51,776 --> 00:04:53,295
(On the attack)
Eating grapes without spitting out the skin.

129
00:04:55,776 --> 00:04:56,336
Yuwen.

130
00:04:57,024 --> 00:04:58,208
(Out)

131
00:04:59,096 --> 00:04:59,520
(Could it be you?)
Yuning.

132
00:04:59,936 --> 00:05:00,672
Yuning, what...

133
00:05:02,193 --> 00:05:03,776
(Could it really be Yuning?)

134
00:05:04,016 --> 00:05:04,856
Is it that easy?

135
00:05:04,856 --> 00:05:05,336
Really?

136
00:05:06,136 --> 00:05:07,216
Hard to guard against.

137
00:05:08,335 --> 00:05:09,056
(Staring intently)

138
00:05:09,136 --> 00:05:09,936
Why are you looking at me?

139
00:05:11,016 --> 00:05:12,576
Take your hands out.

140
00:05:12,867 --> 00:05:13,936
(Well-placed)

141
00:05:13,936 --> 00:05:15,336
What did you say?

142
00:05:15,336 --> 00:05:16,336
I said don't look at me.

143
00:05:17,056 --> 00:05:18,096
As soon as I leaned back,

144
00:05:18,096 --> 00:05:19,456
Yuwen died.

145
00:05:20,856 --> 00:05:21,496
Well,

146
00:05:21,496 --> 00:05:22,216
you leaned back.

147
00:05:22,216 --> 00:05:23,376
But weren't you looking at me?

148
00:05:23,656 --> 00:05:24,616
He was staring.

149
00:05:24,616 --> 00:05:25,496
The killer...

150
00:05:26,096 --> 00:05:26,536
This killer

151
00:05:26,536 --> 00:05:27,696
is quite something.

152
00:05:28,296 --> 00:05:29,216
Pretty impressive.

153
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,600
(Preparing for the third attack)

154
00:05:34,376 --> 00:05:35,040
Xingxu.

155
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,576
Raise your hands. Let me see your table.

156
00:05:37,785 --> 00:05:38,944
(Hunting time)

157
00:05:39,456 --> 00:05:40,256
Xingxu.

158
00:05:42,144 --> 00:05:43,584
(Strange Killer has eliminated everyone)

159
00:05:44,416 --> 00:05:45,016
It's him.

160
00:05:45,016 --> 00:05:45,816
It's him.

161
00:05:45,816 --> 00:05:46,336
It's him.

162
00:05:47,976 --> 00:05:49,376
If I'm the Killer,

163
00:05:49,376 --> 00:05:50,136
would I be this stupid?

164
00:05:50,136 --> 00:05:51,256
Didn't you call his name?

165
00:05:52,016 --> 00:05:52,536
No.

166
00:05:52,936 --> 00:05:53,504
Wait, I did.

167
00:05:53,504 --> 00:05:54,776
He called out my name.

168
00:05:54,776 --> 00:05:57,408
Yeah, calling your name
or pointing at you.

169
00:05:57,408 --> 00:05:58,208
What about you?

170
00:05:58,208 --> 00:06:00,176
He also said my name, right?

171
00:06:00,176 --> 00:06:02,416
You said Yuwen, and she died.

172
00:06:02,416 --> 00:06:03,856
You said Xingxu, and he died.

173
00:06:03,856 --> 00:06:05,416
Yuning, your explanation
is unconvincing.

174
00:06:05,416 --> 00:06:07,016
- It doesn't fit your persona.
- Keep saying that.

175
00:06:07,016 --> 00:06:07,656
And you'll look

176
00:06:07,656 --> 00:06:08,496
absolutely ridiculous.

177
00:06:08,496 --> 00:06:10,056
Let me find out how ridiculous it is.

178
00:06:12,376 --> 00:06:14,016
Be very certain about it.

179
00:06:14,016 --> 00:06:14,336
Okay?

180
00:06:14,336 --> 00:06:15,576
Let's make this more exciting.

181
00:06:15,576 --> 00:06:16,376
Be more certain.

182
00:06:16,376 --> 00:06:17,576
"If Liu Yuning is not the Killer,

183
00:06:17,576 --> 00:06:18,536
I'll do this

184
00:06:18,536 --> 00:06:19,016
or that."

185
00:06:19,016 --> 00:06:20,336
If Liu Yuning is not the killer,

186
00:06:20,336 --> 00:06:21,016
I'll sit down.

187
00:06:23,656 --> 00:06:25,576
If you don't vouch for me,
you're a suspect.

188
00:06:26,144 --> 00:06:27,736
(Suddenly?)

189
00:06:27,736 --> 00:06:28,416
Why is that?

190
00:06:28,896 --> 00:06:29,936
Why am I a suspect?

191
00:06:29,936 --> 00:06:30,456
What?

192
00:06:30,456 --> 00:06:31,816
I didn't do anything.

193
00:06:31,816 --> 00:06:33,216
Because 80% of the time,

194
00:06:33,216 --> 00:06:34,056
you were observing me.

195
00:06:34,056 --> 00:06:36,456
I was trying to form a judgment.

196
00:06:37,696 --> 00:06:38,816
I was thinking about

197
00:06:38,816 --> 00:06:41,696
what you'd ask the poor soul to do.

198
00:06:41,696 --> 00:06:43,776
Make him eat non-stop?

199
00:06:43,776 --> 00:06:44,616
Why is that bad?

200
00:06:44,616 --> 00:06:45,408
That's totally fine.

201
00:06:45,976 --> 00:06:47,256
It's definitely Yuning.

202
00:06:47,256 --> 00:06:48,456
His explanation is unconvincing.

203
00:06:48,456 --> 00:06:50,216
"Why is that bad? That's totally fine."

204
00:06:50,216 --> 00:06:52,296
He's speaking from the perspective

205
00:06:52,296 --> 00:06:53,416
- of the poor soul.
- Yeah.

206
00:06:53,416 --> 00:06:54,096
Makes sense.

207
00:06:55,936 --> 00:06:56,816
Who do you think it is?

208
00:06:56,816 --> 00:06:57,296
I think

209
00:06:57,296 --> 00:06:58,856
it's either you or Honglei.

210
00:06:59,104 --> 00:07:00,056
(Yuning's choice)

211
00:07:00,056 --> 00:07:00,456
No.

212
00:07:00,816 --> 00:07:02,816
His argument is full of holes.

213
00:07:02,816 --> 00:07:04,976
He was trying to change Nai's mind.

214
00:07:04,976 --> 00:07:05,416
Now he says,

215
00:07:05,416 --> 00:07:07,456
"It's either you or Honglei."

216
00:07:09,176 --> 00:07:09,776
He has been

217
00:07:09,776 --> 00:07:11,256
staring at me.

218
00:07:11,816 --> 00:07:13,136
If you still suspect me,

219
00:07:13,136 --> 00:07:14,136
there's something fishy.

220
00:07:14,856 --> 00:07:16,096
I just want to ask one thing.

221
00:07:17,096 --> 00:07:17,656
Yuning.

222
00:07:17,656 --> 00:07:18,456
You just said

223
00:07:18,456 --> 00:07:20,096
that Nai was staring at you

224
00:07:20,096 --> 00:07:20,936
80% of the time.

225
00:07:20,936 --> 00:07:22,416
Then how did he kill anyone?

226
00:07:22,416 --> 00:07:22,976
Exactly.

227
00:07:23,896 --> 00:07:25,096
You're targeting me.

228
00:07:25,096 --> 00:07:26,096
You're also a suspect.

229
00:07:27,216 --> 00:07:28,776
I just think it's you.

230
00:07:31,584 --> 00:07:32,608
(Just watch the show)

231
00:07:32,976 --> 00:07:34,856
Yuning is very logical.

232
00:07:34,856 --> 00:07:35,336
Yes.

233
00:07:35,336 --> 00:07:35,816
Right?

234
00:07:35,816 --> 00:07:37,136
But now his analysis is

235
00:07:37,136 --> 00:07:38,856
- completely illogical.
- Yeah.

236
00:07:40,656 --> 00:07:41,936
If you are innocent,

237
00:07:41,936 --> 00:07:43,016
you would be trying

238
00:07:43,016 --> 00:07:43,936
to look for the killer.

239
00:07:43,936 --> 00:07:45,696
Suspecting me is just too strange.

240
00:07:47,776 --> 00:07:49,336
It's always after he pointed at someone.

241
00:07:49,336 --> 00:07:49,976
I died first.

242
00:07:49,976 --> 00:07:50,576
That's not new.

243
00:07:50,576 --> 00:07:51,296
It could be

244
00:07:51,296 --> 00:07:52,136
a coincidence.

245
00:07:52,136 --> 00:07:52,736
She died second.

246
00:07:52,736 --> 00:07:53,216
The third.

247
00:07:53,216 --> 00:07:54,496
He asked him

248
00:07:54,496 --> 00:07:55,616
to raise his hands.

249
00:07:55,616 --> 00:07:56,576
After that, he died.

250
00:07:56,576 --> 00:07:57,096
Yeah.

251
00:07:57,096 --> 00:07:58,296
If it wasn't him,

252
00:07:58,296 --> 00:07:59,576
he would defend himself, right?

253
00:08:00,056 --> 00:08:00,672
Yeah.

254
00:08:01,056 --> 00:08:03,096
Jingfei, you're doing so well.

255
00:08:03,096 --> 00:08:03,816
Makes sense.

256
00:08:04,033 --> 00:08:04,928
(Feeling wronged)

257
00:08:05,728 --> 00:08:06,616
(Hiding well)

258
00:08:06,616 --> 00:08:07,536
Let me say something.

259
00:08:07,536 --> 00:08:08,456
Why didn't I defend myself?

260
00:08:08,456 --> 00:08:10,216
I've recorded a whole season
with you guys.

261
00:08:10,216 --> 00:08:10,896
I've learned.

262
00:08:12,456 --> 00:08:13,496
Explanations won't help.

263
00:08:13,496 --> 00:08:14,216
That's right.

264
00:08:14,552 --> 00:08:15,296
(Making things worse)

265
00:08:18,456 --> 00:08:20,536
You guys get caught up in your ideas.

266
00:08:20,536 --> 00:08:22,112
You won't listen to anyone.

267
00:08:22,616 --> 00:08:23,856
I trust my feelings.

268
00:08:24,256 --> 00:08:26,216
These people are smart and stubborn.

269
00:08:26,856 --> 00:08:27,656
You know.

270
00:08:29,936 --> 00:08:31,656
The killer played really well.

271
00:08:32,699 --> 00:08:33,504
(Thanks)

272
00:08:33,736 --> 00:08:34,776
Don't praise yourself like that.

273
00:08:34,776 --> 00:08:35,536
Praising yourself?

274
00:08:36,176 --> 00:08:36,416
Well...

275
00:08:36,936 --> 00:08:38,816
The survivors have the right to vote.

276
00:08:38,816 --> 00:08:40,416
Three, two, one.

277
00:08:40,416 --> 00:08:41,056
(Voting time)
Please vote.

278
00:08:43,168 --> 00:08:44,416
(Liu Yuning 3 votes, Gong Jun 2 votes)

279
00:08:44,416 --> 00:08:45,856
Yuning is eliminated.

280
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:46,776
(Out)

281
00:08:46,776 --> 00:08:47,616
The end?

282
00:08:48,256 --> 00:08:49,816
Yuning's role is

283
00:08:51,936 --> 00:08:52,512
a Good Person.

284
00:08:56,544 --> 00:08:58,400
(Innocent)

285
00:09:00,176 --> 00:09:01,536
Really?

286
00:09:02,616 --> 00:09:04,536
(Clearly happy)
So sad. Really.

287
00:09:09,896 --> 00:09:10,688
Lin Yi.

288
00:09:11,176 --> 00:09:12,672
Look into my eyes.

289
00:09:13,656 --> 00:09:15,072
Look into my eyes.

290
00:09:16,495 --> 00:09:17,056
Lin Yi.

291
