- Constantly.

307
00:09:50,016 --> 00:09:51,016
True God of Werewolf Game.

308
00:09:51,016 --> 00:09:51,816
Impressive.

309
00:09:53,016 --> 00:09:53,976
He played well.

310
00:09:53,976 --> 00:09:54,560
