311
00:09:55,016 --> 00:09:55,816
You played well.

312
00:09:56,336 --> 00:09:56,936
Lin Yi.

313
00:09:56,936 --> 00:09:58,656
You look like you're at least

314
00:09:58,656 --> 00:09:59,216
20 years older.

315
00:10:01,496 --> 00:10:03,336
Lin Yi's role is

316
00:10:03,336 --> 00:10:04,056
