335
00:10:38,376 --> 00:10:39,616
I pointed like this.

336
00:10:41,176 --> 00:10:42,336
I pointed at him like this.

337
00:10:43,736 --> 00:10:44,696
But when I was pointing,

338
00:10:44,696 --> 00:10:46,216
