461
00:14:47,376 --> 00:14:48,696
It was too fast.

462
00:14:48,696 --> 00:14:49,296
Too fast.

463
00:14:49,296 --> 00:14:50,496
Everything happened too fast.

464
00:14:50,496 --> 00:14:51,776
