494
00:15:32,656 --> 00:15:33,696
Because you were staring at him
the whole time.

495
00:15:33,696 --> 00:15:34,176
Right.

496
00:15:34,936 --> 00:15:35,616
In my mind,

497
00:15:35,616 --> 00:15:38,216
