498
00:15:38,216 --> 00:15:39,256
Yeah, these two Wens.

499
00:15:39,648 --> 00:15:40,639
(Yuning's choice)
Two Wens.

500
00:15:40,976 --> 00:15:42,592
(Agreeing)
Yeah, that makes sense.

501
00:15:42,856 --> 00:15:44,192
But in my eyes, Naiwen

502
00:15:44,192 --> 00:15:45,536
