like this.

507
00:15:51,536 --> 00:15:51,656
Right.

508
00:15:51,656 --> 00:15:52,776
Very nervous.

509
00:15:53,056 --> 00:15:53,856
(Guilty)

510
00:15:53,856 --> 00:15:54,616
Because I felt

511
00:15:54,616 --> 00:15:56,776
