518
00:16:04,216 --> 00:16:04,736
Like this.

519
00:16:06,096 --> 00:16:07,016
Killing with the tongue.

520
00:16:07,016 --> 00:16:07,976
No, that's too obvious.

521
00:16:10,816 --> 00:16:11,696
