548
00:17:04,936 --> 00:17:05,856
It's possible then.

549
00:17:06,856 --> 00:17:08,016
You're joining them now.

550
00:17:09,616 --> 00:17:11,104
When we hear a logic,

551
00:17:11,104 --> 00:17:12,032
