552
00:17:12,576 --> 00:17:13,456
Yes.

553
00:17:13,456 --> 00:17:14,336
That makes sense.

554
00:17:14,336 --> 00:17:15,216
Analyze it.

555
00:17:15,496 --> 00:17:16,496
I don't want to analyze.

556
00:17:17,416 --> 00:17:18,976
Don't let one defeat

557
00:17:18,976 --> 00:17:20,176
