559
00:17:20,936 --> 00:17:22,776
Last season, we failed many times.

560
00:17:22,776 --> 00:17:23,856
Last season, I never won either.

561
00:17:24,176 --> 00:17:25,696
I never guessed right once.

562
00:17:25,696 --> 00:17:26,776
Never guessed right once.

563
00:17:26,776 --> 00:17:29,184
